name: Cyber Tree Maker
description:
Generative abstract tree maker. Use the following keys to configure your tree.

Tip: You may have to click the tree before the keys work.
Tip 2: Shift+key inverts the key function

Q = Adds branches
W = Adds roots
A = Randomizes branches
S = Randomizes roots
Z = Increases hue of colors
X = Increases saturation of colors
C = Increases light of colors
V = Increases color variability
